title: Barnacles
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Chip shop cafe. Menu has separate section listing all vegetarian and vegan options as of Feb 2011. Staff are knowledgeable about vegetarians, vegans, gluten free options. The chips and veg options are all fried separately. For vegans they offer Linda McCartney sausages, falafels, kebab, humus with salad, chips, pita, jacket potatoes, toast with beans, vegan apple crumble & ice cream, chocolate and vanilla sundae. Roast lunches, full breakfasts. They use soya milk and dairy free spreads.
